data.description: Spread out in this reasonably-priced 1-story home in the Newly Constructed Skyline Flats community. You'll enjoy 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a chic dining room, master suite with walk-in closet for your wardrobe, his-and-her closets, separate shower, dual sinks and a garden tub. Entertain in the spacious formal living room with carpeting, an inviting kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, double sinks, breakfast bar for on-the-go meals. It's 2 years young, move-in ready and screaming for new ownership. This is a must see and won't last long.
